The joint pdf of the two new variables is now

\[g(y_{1},y_{2})=f\left(\frac{y_{1}}{y_{2}},y_{2}\right)\cdot|\det(M)|=\left\{ \begin{array}{cc}\left(\frac{y_{1}}{y_{2}}+y_{2}\right)\cdot\frac{1}{y_{2}}& 0<y_{1}<y_{2},\,0<y_{2}<1\\ 0&\text{otherwise}\end{array}\right.\]

