\[G_{n}(y)=\left[F(y)\right]^{n}\qquad g_{n}(y)=n[F(y)]^{n-1}\cdot f(y)\]

The cdf and pdf of \(Y_{1}\) are

\[G_{1}(y)=1-\left[1-F(y)\right]^{n}\qquad g_{1}(y)=n[1-F(y)]^{n-1}\cdot f(y)\]

