\[E(X^{k}) =\int_{0}^{\infty}x^{k}\frac{x^{(v/2)-1}}{2^{v/2}\Gamma(v/2)}e^{- x/2}dx\] \[=\frac{2^{k+v/2}\Gamma(k+v/2)}{2^{v/2}\Gamma(v/2)}\int_{0}^{ \infty}\frac{x^{(k+v/2)-1}}{2^{k+v/2}\Gamma(k+v/2)}\,e^{-x/2}dx\]

