3. Alternative hypothesis: \(H_{\text{a}}\): \(\mu\neq\) 130 (a departure from the claimed value in _either_ direction is of concern).
4. Test statistic value: \[z=\frac{\overline{x}-\mu_{0}}{\sigma/\sqrt{n}}=\frac{\overline{x}-130}{1.5/ \sqrt{n}}\]
