Therefore,

\[\hat{\mathbf{\rho}}=\left[\mathbf{X}^{\prime}\mathbf{X}\right]^{-1}\mathbf{X}^{\prime}\mathbf{y}= \begin{bmatrix}79/12&-5/2&-1/3\\ -5/2&1&0\\ -1/3&0&2/3\end{bmatrix}\begin{bmatrix}1163\\ 3003\\ 631\end{bmatrix}=\begin{bmatrix}-61.417\\ 95.5\\ 33\end{bmatrix}\]

